I"]<p>Som udgangspunkt findes der 5 breakpoints: extra small, small, medium, large, or extra large.</p>

<h3>Klasser som rammer alle breakpoints</h3>

<p>Brug klassen <code>.col</code> eller <code>.col-*</code> uden responsivt prefix (fx. md).</p>

<div class="component-preview px-4 component-preview-grid-all-breakpoints p-4" aria-label="">
    <div class="container">
    <div class="row mb-2">
        <div class="col-1">
            <div class="align-text-center px-2">1</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-1 ">
            <div class="align-text-center px-2">2</div>
